Data Processing Engine Definitions for Insurance

You transform data available in your Salesforce org and write back transformation results as new or updated records using Data Processing Engine. You can transform standard and custom object data with Data Processing Engine definitions.

Use Data Processing Engine Templates
Prebuilt templates allow you to create datasets that improve sales and extend customer outreach.

Clone Data Processing Engine Templates
You can clone predefined templates and customize them according to your business needs.

Activate a Data Processing Engine Definition
After cloning, you must activate the definitions.
